Blogmeido (blog√√∂∂) is a tiny blogging tool and manage system. using the Belle (http://www.getbelle.com) Theme of wordpress. And rewrite it in Python + Tornado web server.

$python main.py
Open a broswer, type localhost:8888 in the address bar, then you could find it.

Requirement:
    Python 2.7+
    Tornado 2.2.x

Notice:
    You should change the cookies_secret in settings.
